{
  "stem": "25773.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Masia ?] he knew, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, she was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a young Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told us that we should not go by-- travel by-- by trains because it's dangerous, there we can be approached by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We should go through the lanes to this place called [INAUDIBLE], which was-- Krystyna's mother was there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Krystyna's uncle was a rich farmer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was like 120 kilometers from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we embarked on walking by foot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After a short time, we had to walk barefoot because-- because the shoes were torn to pieces.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what we did, we worked early morning till about noon or so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we stopped at the farm which we thought looks nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We approached the peasants.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The peasants in Poland were very nice, unlike the lower middle class, which was [INAUDIBLE] to the nuns, the peasants were fabulous.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They received, as there were a lot of refugees from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no question of Jewish anymore at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they received us very warmly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They gave us a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had to work in the fields, so we learned how to work in the field-- how to dig potatoes, how to-- cucumber, and tomatoes, and cabbage-- endless, endless rows of cabbage, and our back was breaking and we helped.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like that we were slowly going forward and forward.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were f Sometimes we were given a little lift by a cart, and more than often, we-- we had to walk from one farm, from one village, from one village-- 120 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there were advantages, because sometimes we went to a farm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a brook.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- we worked the day-- the half of the day always-- then was a brook.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
